job.title: Vizag Steel Plant Trade Apprentice Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 319 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:319

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Trade Apprentice

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for ITI pass has been published by Vizag Steel Plant for Trade Apprentice vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Trade Apprentice, from 26-06-2021, and till 17-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for Un-Reserved/ OBC/ EWS Candidates category candidates is Rs. 200/-
  • The application fee for SC, ST & PWD Candidates Candidates category candidates is Rs. 100/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Trade Apprentice in Vizag Steel Plant, your ITI must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 26-06-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 17-07-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

Vizag Steel Plant Trade Apprentice Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Vizag Steel Plant Trade Apprentice Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Trade Apprentice. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of Vizag Steel Plant and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Vizag Steel Plant 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
